&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;#x1f44b; Hello friend, &amp;#x1f4dc; &amp;#x1f642; &amp;#x1f3e0;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was looking for a very creative way to wish someone &lt;em&gt;&amp;quot; Happy Birthday &amp;ldquo;&lt;/em&gt; &amp;#x1f389; . As you think we will make some creativity using javascript. also added this to the List of &lt;a class="link" href="https://vanpariyar.in/tools/" title="tools"
 &gt;Tools&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All Code Given Here:- &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/vanpariyar/birthday-wishes/" title="birthday Wishes Tool"
 target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 &gt;Github Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Live demo Here:- &lt;a class="link" href="https://vanpariyar.github.io/birthday-wishes/?name=ShreeHariJI" title="birthday Wishes Tool Live Demo"
 target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 &gt;Live Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id="template"&gt;Template
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can found this HTML template on anywhere, Websites like codepen. I have taken from codepen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;ProTip:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; select very simple first time for learning &amp;#x270b;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;i have chosed once very simple template. i have mentioned in the code. &lt;a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/vanpariyar/birthday-wishes/blob/main/index.html"&gt;My Template Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="how-to-make-tool-dynamic"&gt;How to make tool dynamic
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;If the birthday wishes tool is dynamic then we do not need to make changes every time, so we can send personalized emails from the link like this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://vanpariyar.in/U855XJT_6224387156599252457.png" width="1069" height="667" 
 loading="lazy" alt="demo of personal birthday wishes tool" class="gallery-image"
 data-flex-grow="160"
 data-flex-basis="384px" &gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;if you see we have one attribute &lt;code&gt;?name&lt;/code&gt; in the URL. That is the key to make this dynamic &amp;#x1f60a;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;https://vanpariyar.github.io/birthday-wishes/?name=ShreeHariJI&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;this is our HTML&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;text&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
